<cell id="cell-11"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type>## 5. Link data from Drive

Symlinks to avoid copying the CSVs (~1 GB) into the Colab disk.</cell id="cell-11">
<cell id="cell-12">raw_dir       = f'{REPO_DIR}/grasp-model/data/raw'
processed_dir = f'{REPO_DIR}/grasp-model/data/processed'
